    <section class="issues-container">
        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Game Crashing on Startup</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure your drivers are updated, verify game files, and disable unnecessary
                background apps.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Game Lagging or Low FPS</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Lower game settings, update graphics drivers, and close background
                applications consuming high CPU usage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Game Not Installing</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Check storage space, ensure stable internet, and try reinstalling from a
                different drive.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Multiplayer Connection Issues</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Restart your router, check firewall settings, and ensure the game servers are
                online.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Audio / Sound Problems</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Check audio settings in-game, update sound drivers, and ensure the correct
                output device is selected.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="issue-box">
            <h3>Login Issues</h3>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Reset your password, check server status, and ensure your account details are
                correct.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

